## User POST Request
POST http://localhost:8080/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "John",
    "lastName": "Doe",
    "email": "john.doe@example.com",
    "password": "Password123!"
}

# Create many users
POST http://localhost:8080/users/create-many
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "users": [
        {
            "firstName": "John3",
            "lastName": "Doe",
            "email": "john3.doe@example.com",
            "password": "Password123!"
        },
        {
            "firstName": "John4",
            "lastName": "Doe",
            "email": "john4.doe@example.com",
            "password": "Password123!"
        },
        {
            "firstName": "John4",
            "lastName": "Doe",
            "email": "john5.doe@example.com",
            "password": "Password123!"
        }
    ]
}